"Well, let us hope so. But our doubts will very soon be solved, for here, unless I am much mistaken,
is the person in question."

As he spoke the door opened and a young lady entered the room. She was plainly but neatly dressed,
with a bright, quick face, freckled like a plover's egg, and with the brisk manner of a woman who
has had her own way to make in the world.